  '<div class="disc"><div class="disc-title">GENERAL SALES & REPAIRS DISCLAIMER</div><div class="disc-text">All devices are accepted in good faith. We are not responsible for pre-existing damage, data loss, damage from misuse, liquid damage, or prior third-party repairs. Customers must back up all data before submitting devices. Once a device has left our premises, company liability ceases. By proceeding, the customer accepts these terms.</div></div>'+
